
ALS News today
- User types "ALS News"
- Show a list of social clips from https://alsnewstoday.com/ in the following format:
  Entry_No. Date: Title - URL

  * a social clip object can contain following properties:
    entry_number
    date
    title
    URL
    summary

  After social clips are generated from the website, they are automatically added to an array.
  Then, by their order, each social clip will be assigned an entry number.

  When a user calls these social clips, they are shown as a list.
  The user is able to obtain more information (summary) by entering an entry number; or search for social clips for any particular keyword.
      - the keyword will be search by matching itself to any word in the social clip's actual web contents.

  
